    "description": "<p><strong>TeleRadio</strong> is a global leader in the field of innovative security, specialising in vehicle surveillance solutions and we are located in the west of Singapore.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our corporate objective is to provide every vital infrastructure in the world with a highly reliable and efficient vehicle screening system to protect people and their assets.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>TeleRadio </strong>combines the best minds in hardware and software, and innovation has become the defining feature of our systems. Our team of engineers and support group work at the heart of our clients’ businesses and are constantly improving our solutions to meet their ever-changing needs as we are dedicated to providing the highest quality products and services.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are excited to meet up with highly motivated individuals who share a common passion in the security sector.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
